<body>

    <main>
        <section class="FAQs">
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>1. How do I add a new recipe?</h3>
                <p>To add a new recipe, click on the 'Add Recipe' button located on the Recipe Book page. Fill in the necessary details such as meal name, ingredients, cook time, and description, then click 'Submit' to save your recipe.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>2. Can I edit my recipes?</h3>
                <p>Yes, you can easily edit your recipes. Simply go to your Recipe Book, select the recipe you want to edit, and click the 'Edit' button. After making your changes, click 'Submit' to save the updated recipe.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>3. How do I delete a recipe?</h3>
                <p>To delete a recipe, go to your Recipe Book, select the recipe you want to remove, and click the 'Delete' button. You will be prompted to confirm the deletion before it is permanently removed.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>4. Is my data stored securely?</h3>
                <p>Yes, we take your privacy and security seriously. All your recipes are stored securely in our database using the latest encryption methods, ensuring your data is protected at all times.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>5. Can I share my recipes with others?</h3>
                <p>Yes! You can share your recipes with friends and family. Simply click on the 'Share' button on any recipe page to send the recipe to others via email or social media.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>6. How can I contact support?</h3>
                <p>If you need help or have any issues, please visit our 'Contact Us' page. You can reach out to us via email or fill out the contact form to get in touch with our support team.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

</body>

